	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, one would generally need to make a custom map editor for a specific game. That's possible, but first I'd have to know what data format your engine is using. Or if you haven't figured that out yet, first I'd have to see what an entire map might look like, along with how wide and tall they're allowed to be, so that I can help you design a data format.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


